title: The Breakfast Club Talks Student Debt, Nadine Sutherlannd, and Angela Yee Day
itunes:title: The Breakfast Club Talks Student Debt, Nadine Sutherlannd, and Angela Yee Day
description:
Today on the breakfast club we gave legendary artist, Nadine Sutherland on the show to talk to us about music and growing up musically with Bob Marley. Yee gives us all the updates on President Bidens plan to eliminate college debt and help students more. Charlamagne gives us our Thuraday thoughts and Donkey Of The Day
